{{also|ѫже|оуже}}
==Russian==

===Etymology 1===
From {{der|ru|sla-pro|*ju}} + {{m|sla-pro|*že}}.

====Pronunciation====
* {{audio|ru|Ru-{{PAGENAME}}.ogg|Audio}}
* {{ru-IPA|уже́}}

====Adverb====
{{ru-adv|уже́}}

# [[already]]
#: {{uxi|ru|'''Уже́''' [[по́здно]].|It's '''already''' late.}}
# not [[anymore]], no [[longer]] (in a negative sentence)
#: {{uxi|ru|[[я]] '''уже́''' [[не]] [[мочь|могу́]] [[бежа́ть]]|I can't run any more}}

====Particle====
{{head|ru|particle|head=уже́}}

# {{n-g|emphasises an amount or quantity of something}}
#: {{uxi|ru|[[он|Он]] [[не]] [[спать|спал]] '''уже́''' [[второй|втору́ю]] [[ночь]].|It's the second he didn't sleep./He didn't sleep two nights in a row.}}
# {{n-g|emphasises a certain word or collocation}}
#: {{uxi|ru|'''Уже́''' [[по]] [[звук|зву́ку]] [[двигатель|дви́гателя]] [[мо́жно]] [[определи́ть]], [[что]] [[он]] [[неисправный|неиспра́вен]].|By the sound of the engine alone one can determine that it's faulty.}}

====Derived terms====
* {{l|ru|уже́ли}}, {{l|ru|уже́ль}}
* {{l|ru|неуже́ли}}, {{l|ru|неуже́ль}}

====Related terms====
* {{l|ru|ужо́}}
* {{l|ru|уж}}
* {{l|ru|же}}

===Etymology 2===
From {{inh|ru|sla-pro|*ǫže}}.

====Pronunciation====
* {{ru-IPA|у́же|pos=com}}

====Adverb====
{{ru-comparative|у́же}}

# {{comparative of|ru|POS=adjective|у́зкий}}
#: {{uxi|ru|[[этот|Э́та]] [[у́лица]] '''у́же''', [[чем]] [[тот|та́]].|This street is '''narrower''' than that one.}}
# {{comparative of|ru|POS=adverb|у́зко}}

===Etymology 3===
From {{inh|ru|sla-pro|*ǫži}} (ending taken from the hard paradigm).

====Pronunciation====
* {{audio|ru|Ru-{{PAGENAME}}.ogg|audio}}
* {{ru-IPA|уже́}}

====Noun====
{{ru-noun form|уже́|m-an}}

# {{inflection of|ru|уж||pre|s}}

